# Tests

Tests can be found in the `test` folder. They use pythons `unittest` and can be run with:
```
python3 -m unittest path/to/test.py
```

Tests get automatically run after each push.

### Available tests
- Mongo model
- Mongo sorting
- Redis task
    - Basic functions
    - Chaining
